snippet.title: Hakuoki: Kyoka-Roku - "Conversation in the Rain" V1 - Intro + Saito Eng translation
snippet.description:
English translation of the first "Conversation in the Rain" story from Hakuoki Kyoka Roku (薄桜鬼 鏡花録), and what happens when you choose Saito. 

My translation may not be 100% accurate since I don't translate from Japanese. 

Video made for entertainment purposes only. I own nothing aside from the translation.
